g.text: 1. At each schedule, it performs the search for new news
2. Search for news in configured services
3. Extract the metadata and save it in the local database
4. Download the image related to the news, resize it, create a thumbnail and host it in the archive with a public link for 7 days
5. Inserts news metadata into the cache to speed consumption by the Executor
6. Publish a notification about recent news in Kafka
